{"about_the_game":"<i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i> is a real-time strategy game, developed by one person, in which you will have to collect resources, build your base, train your army by choosing your soldiers wisely and fight. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/SYNOPSIS-SteamStore.png?t=1649164133\" /><br><i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i> tells the story of the fateful historical moment when Russia breaks off diplomatic relations and annexes Ukraine under the closed eyes of the United Nations. As Europe is about to explode, Belarus, Russia's next target, organizes itself to fight for its sovereignty. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/GAMEPLAY-SteamStore.png?t=1649164133\" /><br>In <i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i> you will have to collect resources to expand your base and form your platoon. Your base will offer you a large choice of buildings and units, each unit has its strengths and weaknesses. Scattered around the world, you will find strategic points that you will have to capture to make vehicles spawn. You must then assign soldiers to use them.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/gif_capture.gif?t=1649164133\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/FEATURE-SteamStore.png?t=1649164133\" /><br>What offers <i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i>:  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An interesting and unique story!  <br></li><li>Small-scale combat. Optimize your infantry platoon. <br></li><li>Strategic combat with a cover system for infantry.  <br></li><li>5 factions each with special units and bonuses.  <br></li><li>A large choice of infantry and drone units.  <br></li><li>4 resources with 3 different types of collection.  <br></li><li>Colorful environments.  <br></li><li>A modern war context.</li></ul>  <br><br>What does <strong>not</strong> offer <i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i>:  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Very large scale combat.  <br></li><li>Direct control of units.  <br></li><li>A destructible environment.  <br></li><li>A 360\u00b0 rotation of the camera.  <br></li><li>Several difficulty levels for the campaign mode.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/gif_attack.gif?t=1649164133\" /><br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1123500/extras/TEAM-SteamStore.png?t=1649164133\" /><br><i>Hell of Men: Blood Brothers</i> developed by Whacky Squad Studio and support by 10Loups Games.  <br><br>We love to get constructive feedback on the game, what you like and what you would like to improve. So contact us!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/5821958fa5832f18d0a8a00cc9aed95d1402e1d3.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/2c1cd81de8beec28c39a43a0338ac3f22393b046.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/e4b76339770f9193ab862865f1f1ebcef90db1d1.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/52b2f8e7d7db0166c7c3c1018d0320769f3e82ef.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/59f9c21ae56945520c4c0628560eb314a00aa309.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1123500/b28eaaab5d56d9f10e4d971e8537454b78d5ba33.jpg"},{"name":"Blood Brothers #6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/